\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6}{\ignorespaces Training-free spatial repair for CLIP-based open-vocabulary segmentation. Self-self attention based methods replace CLIP's original last-layer attention to improve patch coherence, while VFM-attention based methods borrow attention maps from an external vision foundation model. CLIPer instead fuses early-layer CLIP information to form a coarse text-aligned segmentation map and then applies fine-grained compensation to recover local details~\citep  {lsunCliperHierarchicallyImproving2025}.}}{25}{figure.6}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:open-vocab-cliper}{{6}{25}{Training-free spatial repair for CLIP-based open-vocabulary segmentation. Self-self attention based methods replace CLIP's original last-layer attention to improve patch coherence, while VFM-attention based methods borrow attention maps from an external vision foundation model. CLIPer instead fuses early-layer CLIP information to form a coarse text-aligned segmentation map and then applies fine-grained compensation to recover local details~\citep {lsunCliperHierarchicallyImproving2025}}{figure.6}{}}
