\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {11}{\ignorespaces OneRef's one-tower referring model. The image branch applies referring-aware dynamic image masking, while the text branch masks the words related to the referred target. A shared multi-head self-attention encoder feeds referring mask image modeling and referring mask language modeling heads, which reconstruct visual content and language content while scoring target-relation consistency~\citep  {xiaoOnerefUnifiedOnetower2024}.}}{36}{figure.11}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:promptable-oneref}{{11}{36}{OneRef's one-tower referring model. The image branch applies referring-aware dynamic image masking, while the text branch masks the words related to the referred target. A shared multi-head self-attention encoder feeds referring mask image modeling and referring mask language modeling heads, which reconstruct visual content and language content while scoring target-relation consistency~\citep {xiaoOnerefUnifiedOnetower2024}}{figure.11}{}}
